# Perfil UI

- Reuse `src/components/ui/*` — do not add raw `<button>`/`<input>` with duplicate classes.
- Business logic in `src/hooks/`, not in `App.tsx`.
- Profile field labels: `src/shared/profile-fields.ts` only.
- Messages: `sendMessage` from `@/shared/messages`.
